{{gherdëina}}[[File:St_Peter_in_Lajen_von_der_Katzenleiter.jpg|miniatura|Ududa de San Piere.]]'''San Piere''' ([[lingaz tudësch|tudësch]]: ''St. Peter'', [[lingaz talian|talian]]: ''San Pietro'') ie na [[frazion (Talia)|frazion]] dl chemun de [[Laion]] te [[Südtirol]], [[Talia]]. [[Geografia|Geograficamënter]] iel te la [[valeda]] de [[Gherdëina]], ma da n pont de ududa soziel ne vëniel nia cuntà pra Gherdëina, ajache a San Piere ne vëniel nia rujenà [[ladin]]. San Piere ie zirca 3 km a vest de [[Pontives]], l cunfin linguistich de Gherdëina.
